Class Response

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.krobothsoftware.commons.network.Response
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResponseAuthenticate, ResponseRedirect

    public class Response
extends Object
    Response holder from RequestBuilder.execute(NetworkHelper). Make sure to call close() to ensure connection is closed.
    Since:
    SNC 1.0
    See Also:
    RequestBuilder.execute(NetworkHelper)
